    "steam_appid": 3211790,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211790/extras/e72590e51a38a9987f755684fa2b6b5f.avif?t=1728463897\" width=552 height=258 /></span><strong>SSATNOTMM</strong> is a <strong>small action game with roguelite elements</strong>. Survive waves of enemies, buy permanent upgrades, befriend colorful characters, die and do it all over again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211790/extras/b1bf67121230f9a8ad166d1ddf60482c.apng?t=1728463897\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211790/extras/b1bf67121230f9a8ad166d1ddf60482c.poster.avif?t=1728463897\" class=\"bb_img\" width=344 height=124 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➤ Jump, dash and kill with <strong>fast-paced 2D shooter gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➤ Fight enemy waves made from <strong>11</strong> different types of monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➤ Survive <strong>4</strong> types of hazards ranging from acid rains to murderous buzz saws.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➤ Mix and match <strong>22</strong> arcana cards with unique effects as you level up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➤ Purchase up to <strong>16</strong> permanent upgrades and become unstoppable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➤ Combine and use <strong>14</strong> different items to help you deal with the horde.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➤ Meet and befriend <strong>7</strong> quirky characters.</p>",
